Shiitake Cottage Pie with Cauliflower Mash

pinterest.com4

Aug 26, 2020 - This completely plant-based take on a traditional cottage pie will blow your socks off. It’s full of shiitake mushrooms which means it packs a meaty punch.

  • 2 Bay leaves
  • 1⁄2 Carrot
  • 550 g Cauliflower florets
  • 1 Celery stick
  • 1 clove Garlic
  • 1⁄2 Red onion
  • 40 g Shiitake mushrooms, dried
  • 1⁄2 tsp Thyme, dried
  • 1 tbsp Tomato puree
  • 500 ml Vegetable stock or bouillon, vegan
  • 2 tbsp Soy sauce, dark
  • 70 g Vegan butter
  • 2 tbsp Flour, plain white
  • 1 Pinch Sea salt, flaky
  • 2 tbsp Vegetable oil
  • 100 ml Red wine, vegan
